snippet.title: Stellar Wanderer DX - Announcement Trailer (PC/Nintendo Switch/PlayStation/Xbox)
snippet.description:
Fight, trade, and explore a vast open-world universe.

Old-school space simulation Stellar Wanderer DX launches 2024 on PC, Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S, and Xbox One!

Official website: https://leoful.com/stellar-wanderer-dx-en
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1401630/
